// Dragnet [Ransomware]: dragnet-ransomware-2026-1166 — Mass File Rename (thegentlemen)
// Status: stable | Level: high | ID: 2f93c796-3253-587a-8d66-582bf5399499

#event_simpleName=*
| (FilePath = *.encrypted OR FilePath = *.locked OR FilePath = *.ransom)
| table([timestamp, ComputerName])
| limit(1000)
